data.description: Fabulous Home! When you enter this stunning home, you are welcomed to an open floor plan. The home features a popular white-on-white kitchen with gold accents and pulls, quartz counters, island overlooking the spacious living room. The Chef's kitchen also features all-white upgraded KitchenAid appliances. Livingroom has a beautifully coffered ceiling and shiplap accent wall! Hardwood floors on the main floor. Separate dining rm w/ upscale accents & coffered ceilings. One bedroom on the 1st floor & the owner's suite upstairs. Owners suite features a sitting room, soaking tub, separate shower, & spacious closets! Laundry off the hall upstairs near the owner's suite! The back porch offers a private oasis to enjoy morning coffee and evening cocktails with white drapes and a Charleston-style swing bed. ** TWO 62 Gallon HOT water heaters!! The home situated at the end of the street means little traffic. Canterbury Farms offers an Olympic-sized swimming pool, play area, and walking trails. The refrigerator, chandeliers & porch swing remain.
